OL,7,F, owned by Britannia Jinky Jersey
OL,8,FLimited, was found to have
OL,9,Fdiscriminated against Irish Travellers
OL,10,Fwho tried to book stays at its resorts
OL,11,FThe Equality and Human Rights
OL,12,FCommission (EHRC) said.
OL,14,FIt also found Irish Travellers and
OL,15,Fpeople associated with them were
OL,16,Flisted as 'undesirables'.
