OL,7,FPontins also introduced a rule
OL,8,Frequiring guests to appear on the
OL,9,Felectoral register, a practice found
OL,10,Fto be discriminatory against
OL,11,FTravellers, who are less likely to be
OL,12,Fon the register.
OL,14,FThe EHRC argues this amounts to
OL,15,Fseveral breaches of the Equality Act.
