OL,7,FThe business has been served with an
OL,8,Funlawful act notice by the
OL,9,Forganisation due to the "multiple
OL,10,Finstances of race discrimination
OL,11,Fagainst Irish Travellers" uncovered
OL,12,Fduring its investigation.
OL,14,FThe EHRC said it was first alerted to
OL,15,Fthese practices by a whistle blower in
OL,16,F2020 which led to the equality
OL,17,Fwatchdog entering into a legally
OL,18,Fbinding agreement with Pontins in
OL,19,F2021, to end the practices and prevent
OL,20,Ffurther discrimination.
