OL,7,FHowever, after Pontins failed to
OL,8,Fcomply with the agreement's terms, the
OL,9,FEHRC terminated the agreement in 2022
OL,10,Fand launched a formal investigation.
OL,12,FPontins has recently closed three of
OL,13,Fits venues without warning.
OL,15,FIn December it announced its in East
OL,16,FSussex, and , would close with
OL,17,Fimmediate effect, while in January it
OL,18,Fsaid its was also now closed.
OL,20,FAfter having 30 parks in its heyday,
OL,21,Fonly three sites now remain.
