OL,7,FBaroness Kishwer Falkner, chairwoman
OL,8,Fof the EHRC, said the investigation
OL,9,Fhad found "shocking overt race
OL,10,Fdiscrimination".
OL,12,F"Our investigation into Pontins
OL,13,Funcovered flagrant breaches of the
OL,14,FEquality Act 2010," she said.
OL,16,F"Their business practices demonstrated
OL,17,Fshocking overt race discrimination
OL,18,Ftowards Irish Travellers and there was
OL,19,Fa culture of denial.
