OL,7,F"We remain deeply concerned about
OL,8,Fthese discriminatory practices. They
OL,9,Fwere instigated and supported by
OL,10,Fsenior managers and their leadership
OL,11,Ffailed to take any action or accept
OL,12,Fcorporate responsibility.
OL,14,F"Such unlawful and discriminatory
OL,15,Fbehaviour is completely unacceptable,
OL,16,Fand it must never be tolerated."
