OL,7,FChris McDonagh, campaigns officer at
OL,8,FFriends, Families and Travellers,
OL,9,Fsaid: "It is deeply saddening that
OL,10,FIrish Traveller people have become so
OL,11,Fused to hate and prejudice that the
OL,12,FPontins 'blacklist' did not come as a
OL,13,Fsurprise.
OL,15,F"Whilst we are certain that Pontins
OL,16,Fare not the only ones operating such
OL,17,Fdiscriminatory policies, we welcome
OL,18,Fthe EHRC's investigation and commend
OL,19,Fthe whistleblower's principled stance.
OL,20,FEveryone deserves to live free from
OL,21,Fhate and prejudice."
